---
import Tool from '../../layouts/Tool.astro';
---

<Tool
	title="PDF Unlock Tool – Remove PDF Password Online Free | SinzTools"
	description="Remove password protection from PDF files online for free. Enter your PDF password and unlock it instantly in your browser. No uploads, 100% private."
	tool="pdf-unlock"
>
<style>
.password-field {
	position: relative;
	margin: 16px 0;
}
.password-field label {
	display: block;
	font-weight: 600;
	margin-bottom: 6px;
	color: #374151;
}
.password-input-wrap {
	display: flex;
	gap: 8px;
	align-items: center;
}
.password-input-wrap input[type="password"],
.password-input-wrap input[type="text"] {
	flex: 1;
	padding: 10px 14px;
	border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
	border-radius: 6px;
	font-size: 15px;
	outline: none;
	transition: border-color 0.15s;
}
.password-input-wrap input:focus {
	border-color: #2563eb;
	box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(37,99,235,0.1);
}
.toggle-pw {
	padding: 10px 14px;
	border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
	border-radius: 6px;
	background: #f9fafb;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	color: #6b7280;
	transition: background 0.15s;
}
.toggle-pw:hover {
	background: #f1f5f9;
	color: #374151;
}
.pdf-file-info {
	background: #f8f9fa;
	border-left: 4px solid #2563eb;
	border-radius: 4px;
	padding: 14px 16px;
	margin: 16px 0;
}
.pdf-file-info-row {
	display: flex;
	gap: 6px;
	margin-bottom: 4px;
	font-size: 14px;
}
.pdf-file-info-row:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.pdf-file-info-label { font-weight: 600; color: #6b7280; min-width: 50px; }
.pdf-file-info-value { color: #111827; word-break: break-all; }
.unlock-btn {
	background: #2563eb;
	color: white;
	border: none;
	padding: 12px 28px;
	border-radius: 6px;
	cursor: pointer;
	font-size: 15px;
	font-weight: 600;
	display: flex;
	align-items: center;
	gap: 8px;
	margin-top: 4px;
	transition: background 0.15s;
}
.unlock-btn:hover:not(:disabled) { background: #1d4ed8; }
.unlock-btn:disabled { background: #93c5fd; cursor: not-allowed; }
.unlock-btn .icon { width: 18px; height: 18px; }
.unlock-form { margin-top: 20px; }
</style>

<a href="#main-content" class="skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
<h1>PDF Unlock Tool</h1>
<p>Remove password protection from a PDF file. Upload your locked PDF, enter the password, and download an unlocked copy — all processed locally in your browser.</p>

<div class="privacy-note">
	<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon">
		<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75 11.25 15 15 9.75m-3-7.036A11.959 11.959 0 0 1 3.598 6 11.99 11.99 0 0 0 3 9.749c0 5.592 3.824 10.29 9 11.623 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.623 0-1.31-.21-2.571-.598-3.751h-.152c-3.196 0-6.1-1.248-8.25-3.285Z"/>
	</svg>
	Runs locally — no uploads. Your PDF and password never leave your device.
</div>

<div class="drop-zone" id="dropZone">
	<input type="file" id="fileInput" accept="application/pdf" style="display: none;">
	<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon">
		<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 16.5V9.75m0 0 3 3m-3-3-3 3M6.75 19.5a4.5 4.5 0 0 1-1.41-8.775 5.25 5.25 0 0 1 10.233-2.33 3 3 0 0 1 3.758 3.848A3.752 3.752 0 0 1 18 19.5H6.75Z"/>
	</svg>
	<p>Drop a PDF file here or <label for="fileInput">browse</label></p>
	<small style="color:#6b7280;">Password-protected PDF files only</small>
</div>

<div id="pdfInfo" class="pdf-file-info" style="display:none;">
	<div class="pdf-file-info-row">
		<span class="pdf-file-info-label">File:</span>
		<span class="pdf-file-info-value" id="pdfName"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="pdf-file-info-row">
		<span class="pdf-file-info-label">Size:</span>
		<span class="pdf-file-info-value" id="pdfSize"></span>
	</div>
</div>

<div class="unlock-form" id="unlockForm" style="display:none;">
	<div class="password-field">
		<label for="pdfPassword">PDF Password</label>
		<div class="password-input-wrap">
			<input type="password" id="pdfPassword" placeholder="Enter the PDF password" autocomplete="off">
			<button type="button" class="toggle-pw" id="togglePw" aria-label="Show/hide password">
				<svg id="eyeIcon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" width="18" height="18">
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.036 12.322a1.012 1.012 0 0 1 0-.639C3.423 7.51 7.36 4.5 12 4.5c4.638 0 8.573 3.007 9.963 7.178.07.207.07.431 0 .639C20.577 16.49 16.64 19.5 12 19.5c-4.638 0-8.573-3.007-9.964-7.178Z"/>
					<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 12a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z"/>
				</svg>
			</button>
		</div>
	</div>

	<button class="unlock-btn" id="unlockBtn">
		<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true" class="icon">
			<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 9 0v3.75M3.75 21.75h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H3.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Z"/>
		</svg>
		Unlock PDF
	</button>

	<div class="loading" id="loading">
		<div class="spinner"></div>
		<p>Unlocking PDF...</p>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="errorMessage" class="error-message"></div>
<div id="output"></div>

<h2>How the PDF Unlock tool works</h2>
<p>This tool uses the pdf-lib library, running entirely in your browser, to open your password-protected PDF with the password you provide. It then saves a new copy with no password protection. Your PDF file and your password are never sent to any server — everything happens locally on your device.</p>

<h2>When to use this tool</h2>
<p>Use this tool when you have a PDF you own and know the password for, but want to remove the password requirement for easier access. This tool will not bypass or guess unknown passwords — you must provide the correct password yourself.</p>
</Tool>
